Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:08.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Waka, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:22.71,Main,,0,0,0,,See? It's going... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:25.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Waka, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:34.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Work!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you working?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Waka, I'll do it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay. You can do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Waka, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:00.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mari! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:03.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Cream everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:14.51,Main,,0,0,0,,How delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:19.43,Main,,0,0,0,,But it must have hurt to have\NMr. Mixer die in the line of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:22.60,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I think it's still functional.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:26.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? Time for a miraculous recovery?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,The batteries just ran out. They're old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:32.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom's so bad at maintaining things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:35.19,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:37.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You took it without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:39.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You're in no place to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:41.70,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:46.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I left her a note to say that\NI was making crepes with Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:49.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:54.30,Main,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's readable now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:34.44,Main,,0,0,0,,"Episode 4\NVolta on the Battlefield"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:38.07,Main,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't say anything\Nabout this machine.\N"Episode 4\NVolta on the Battlefield"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Shun, may I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing happened, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:56.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess you can't go back to\Nsomewhere you've already been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:04:00.17,Main,,0,0,0,,The one thing that's clear is that this book
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.26,Main,,0,0,0,,and that machine are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,And Mari's pendant, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.06,Main,,0,0,0,,After Mr. Franklin comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Alessandro Volta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:30.87,Main,,0,0,0,,What was that girl thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.37,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Year 1800\N(what is now) Pavia, Italy"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,As I just explained,\N"The Year 1800\N(what is now) Pavia, Italy"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I have filled this with flammable gas,\N"The Year 1800\N(what is now) Pavia, Italy"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I have filled this with flammable gas,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.30,Main,,0,0,0,,plugging it with a cork.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:44.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, using this electrophorus,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I charge up the electricity, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll release the electricity\Ninside this electric pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Could you get\Na little further away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Truly incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:48.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.87,Main,,0,0,0,,This is magnificent, Volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you a magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Volta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:02.09,Main,,0,0,0,,He might be a great scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She's gone again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:23.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Another traveler from\Nthe future's Far East, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Another?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:28.99,Main,,0,0,0,,A few days ago, a man\Nbarged into my laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,He said he was from the future.\NI assumed he was mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:39.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Was his name Eiji... Eiji Hayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Eiji? I don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:44.63,Main,,0,0,0,,That man might have been my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:49.09,Main,,0,0,0,,He's a scientist, and... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:52.72,Main,,0,0,0,,...he'd be wearing a pendant like mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Leone! What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the Austrian soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, have mercy! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop lollygagging! Carry it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Darling! Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Those who refuse to help deserve no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:25.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:31.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.68,Main,,0,0,0,,If you take that, I can't do my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:36.93,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to blame someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:40.81,Main,,0,0,0,,blame the French invaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.19,Main,,0,0,0,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.73,Main,,0,0,0,,To the north of this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:53.07,Main,,0,0,0,,the invading French army is fighting the\NAustrian occupation forces stationed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Really. It's such an annoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.16,Main,,0,0,0,,We're commandeering this for the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:05.00,Main,,0,0,0,,We've been dispatched here\Nfrom Austria to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Any who don't cooperate\Nwill be treated as collaborators,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.96,Main,,0,0,0,,and shown no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.14,Main,,0,0,0,,What? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not Mari's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:35.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Brother has that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari has her golden pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that mean this is mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,"Team Time Travelers"\NDoes that mean this is mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:42.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that mean this is mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:46.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mari's dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:46.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Waka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:53.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Help me find the manual for this machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You can look in those cabinets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Right. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,That man is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari? Is that you, Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:41.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You smell like cake, just like your mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:44.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you really Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa... you really were\Ntraveling through time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:52.07,Main,,0,0,0,,We hadn't heard from you for three years,\Nso everyone was worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:53.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.86,Main,,0,0,0,,An armillary compass?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari, who gave this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Who? It was you, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm gone, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:10.21,Main,,0,0,0,,This armillary compass\Nwill always show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:15.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I must be from before I gave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm your papa from when you\Nwere in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:25.68,Main,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.73,Main,,0,0,0,,means you found the\Nbasement of my laboratory?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Right now it's a secret\Nbetween me, Waka, and Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,But we don't know how to use that machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't know how to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Then how did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:47.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that enough father-daughter time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:55.17,Main,,0,0,0,,My business with you is\Nfar more important right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we ready the electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.01,Main,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.85,Main,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.97,Main,,0,0,0,,As I thought, it's not moving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.94,Main,,0,0,0,,The appearance of that girl
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:16.11,Main,,0,0,0,,inclines me to believe you a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't protect you if you don't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:31.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Due to my clumsiness, Napoleon's return\Nto the Italian front was delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,If I don't protect you, history will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Napoleon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:44.22,Main,,0,0,0,,In a few years, he will conquer Europe\Nand become its emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Under his patronage,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,you will make revolutionary\Ninventions and discoveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:55.36,Main,,0,0,0,,But as things are now, you'll end up\Nbeing shot by an Austrian soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,and die tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:03.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You're saying that because you're from the\Nfuture, you know what's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.12,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:10.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Move! No mercy to those who get in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Professor! The Austrian soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:26.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't move! We'll shoot anyone who resists!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:39.73,Main,,0,0,0,,We've discovered the source of the money\NDr. Hayase used to repay his research funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:42.78,Main,,0,0,0,,A jade cup of Napoleon,\Nwhich sold for $100 million
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:46.07,Main,,0,0,0,,at Sotheby's three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:49.70,Main,,0,0,0,,was sent there by\NDr. Hayase to be sold at auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:53.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Napoleon's jade cup? Was it genuine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's the expert's opinion from Sotheby's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I believe it must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Investigate a little further.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:09.22,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a sacred university!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you are the Austrian army,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:14.10,Main,,0,0,0,,this is no place for such\Noutrageous behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:15.98,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:20.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Marco! How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.49,Main,,0,0,0,,A French prisoner of war has escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:32.99,Main,,0,0,0,,We received information\Nthat he's hiding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:36.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you seen any suspicious individuals?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... I guess I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.05,Main,,0,0,0,,When I give the signal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:54.81,Main,,0,0,0,,wind the knob at the bottom\Nof the armillary compass clockwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Knob? Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,And when you get back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,tell Shun to press the triangle button\Nin the middle of the keyboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.74,Main,,0,0,0,,That should teach him\Nthe basic system controls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going back, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to when\Nyou were in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:20.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to give you that armillary compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Turn the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.01,Main,,0,0,0,,...knob!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:33.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You jerks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:38.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You really shot, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Electric Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:47.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Papa, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.60,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to shoot, then shoot me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,But if you're willing to use a\Nweapon like this on someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,...that means you're prepared\Nto die yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.07,Main,,0,0,0,,That hurts, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:45.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine, so go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:03.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Sh-Sh-She disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,We are the gods who protect this Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell your superiors...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:13.41,Main,,0,0,0,,If you harm these people, I will\Nbring great ruin upon Austria!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.13,Main,,0,0,0,,The bullet is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Are they...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. They're not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:51.61,Main,,0,0,0,,A powerful electric shock has just\Nknocked them temporarily unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:54.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It's another new invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,No... I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:03.79,Main,,0,0,0,,If that's from the future,\NI don't think I should touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:06.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Very prudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.76,Main,,0,0,0,,What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.51,Main,,0,0,0,,They're plans for an electric generator
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.30,Main,,0,0,0,,that uses two types of metal and brine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.85,Main,,0,0,0,,This is where everything begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:24.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I kept you safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,May I ask you one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:33.53,Main,,0,0,0,,How can you be unharmed\Nafter taking all those shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Protective clothing made\Nfrom super-light metals
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,and artificial fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It provides over five times the protection\Nas the same weight of steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That's how.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:52.30,Main,,0,0,0,,The future... it's like a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.93,Main,,0,0,0,,And just one last thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Science enriches society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,But if used in the wrong way,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,it can cause irreversible problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I just wanted you to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:11.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Speaking from personal experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:24.24,Main,,0,0,0,,If you ever interfere with these\Npeople again, I'll show no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I can appear at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,The future of humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:53.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean you met the doctor from\Nbefore his three-year disappearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Theoretically, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:06.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It's possible that the pages of places\Nyou've traveled to stop responding
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:11.25,Main,,0,0,0,,to prevent a time paradox where\Nyou meet yourself in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:16.50,Main,,0,0,0,,This is all a little too complicated\Nfor me to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.01,Main,,0,0,0,,"100 Yen Shop\NStar King"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!\N"100 Yen Shop\NStar King"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna buy batteries.\N"100 Yen Shop\NStar King"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:23.30,Main,,0,0,0,,"100 Yen Shop\NStar King"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:30.56,Main,,0,0,0,,The smell of the gunpowder was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I know I've mentioned this before,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,but I don't think you should tell\Nyour mother about time traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:47.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it will just worry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:55.88,Main,,0,0,0,,So there does appear to be\Nsomething in that laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:59.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you seize the building\Nfor contract violation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for dinner,\Nso wash your hands and get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I set it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, take this too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that girl lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that girl lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,The voltic pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:36.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Invented by the Italian physicist,\NAlessandro Volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Cloth soaked in brine is sandwiched between
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:44.09,Main,,0,0,0,,many alternating plates of copper and zinc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:49.10,Main,,0,0,0,,This results in continuous electric\Ngeneration not previously possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:52.39,Main,,0,0,0,,This invention contributed greatly to\Nfuture experiments requiring electricity,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:56.44,Main,,0,0,0,,and the understanding of electricity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:58.82,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the history Papa\Nwas trying to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:01.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari! Dinnertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:08.07,Main,,0,0,0,,A mille crepes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.20,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right! Sit on down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.96,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my latest offering.\NTaste-test it for me after dinner, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.96,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:23.46,Main,,0,0,0,,A mille crepes cake is just made of crepes,\Nbut what you put between them
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:26.30,Main,,0,0,0,,changes the flavor and texture substantially.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:29.05,Main,,0,0,0,,It's been a bit of trial and error.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:34.14,Main,,0,0,0,,A mille crepes is kind of\Nlike the voltaic pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.10,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:39.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's the first battery ever invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:42.69,Main,,0,0,0,,He tried stacking up all kinds of materials,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:46.49,Main,,0,0,0,,and after lots of trial and error,\Nhe figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:49.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Alessandro Volta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:52.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You're becoming a lot like your papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:54.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Long ago, he said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.54,Main,,0,0,0,,It was as if he'd gone to see it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:04.34,Main,,0,0,0,,He told me all about the invention\Nand the history of its discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:08.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, I'll never\Nforget that Volta person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:13.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Is Papa really off on a research expedition?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:17.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing. It's nothing. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's eat dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:21.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:23.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.65,0:22:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,This pasta is really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.20,Main,,0,0,0,,This pasta is really delicious!\N"Next Episode:\NDisheartened Faraday"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:29.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Really delicious!\N"Next Episode:\NDisheartened Faraday"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:29.82,Main,,0,0,0,,"Next Episode:\NDisheartened Faraday"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:00.46,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mari and Waka's Quick Science"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari and Waka's Quick Science!\N"Mari and Waka's Quick Science"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:03.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Mari and Waka's Quick Science!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:03.96,Main,,0,0,0,,"Copper Plate\NZinc Plate\NCloth soaked in brine"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:07.59,Main,,0,0,0,,The voltic pile Mr. Volta first thought of\N"Copper Plate\NZinc Plate\NCloth soaked in brine"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:12.01,Main,,0,0,0,,is made of layers of cloth soaked in brine,\N"Copper Plate\NZinc Plate\NCloth soaked in brine"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.01,0:24:14.47,Main,,0,0,0,,sandwiched between many\Nplates of copper and zinc.\N"Copper Plate\NZinc Plate\NCloth soaked in brine"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.47,0:24:14.51,Main,,0,0,0,,"Copper Plate Sulfuric Acid Zinc Plate"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:17.81,Main,,0,0,0,,He later refined it to use\Nplates of copper and zinc\N"Copper Plate Sulfuric Acid Zinc Plate"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:21.81,Main,,0,0,0,,placed directly in dilute sulfuric acid.\N"Copper Plate Sulfuric Acid Zinc Plate"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.81,0:24:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,That's our modern-day battery.\N"Copper Plate Sulfuric Acid Zinc Plate"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you know\Nabout this experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.81,0:24:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Electrolysis of water, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.03,0:24:31.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.94,0:24:34.20,Main,,0,0,0,,When you apply electricity to water,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,it splits it into oxygen and hydrogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.28,0:24:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,"Oxygen Hydrogen"\Nit splits it into oxygen and hydrogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.32,0:24:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,"Oxygen Hydrogen"\NThis became possible with the\Ncreation of the voltaic battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:41.33,Main,,0,0,0,,This became possible with the\Ncreation of the voltaic battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.33,0:24:44.12,Main,,0,0,0,,And if the hydrogen and\Noxygen created this way
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.12,0:24:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,are locked in a tube and ignited...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.59,0:24:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It glows!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.75,0:24:52.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it cloudy inside that tube?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.30,0:24:54.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It's because the explosion\Nof the chemical combination\N"Water vapor\NH H\NO" "Chemical Bonding Ignition" "H H O"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.72,0:24:57.01,Main,,0,0,0,,between the hydrogen and oxygen inside\N"Water vapor\NH H\NO" "Chemical Bonding Ignition" "H H O"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.01,0:25:00.56,Main,,0,0,0,,creates water vapor within the tube.\N"Water vapor\NH H\NO" "Chemical Bonding Ignition" "H H O"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.56,0:25:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,"Water vapor\NH H\NO" "Chemical Bonding Ignition" "H H O"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.85,0:25:02.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's believed that electricity\Nis generated at this time.\N"Water vapor\NH H\NO" "Chemical Bonding Ignition" "H H O"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.48,0:25:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,It's believed that electricity\Nis generated at this time.\N"Electric Energy"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.90,0:25:07.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I know that one!\N"Electric Energy"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.23,0:25:08.98,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a fuel cell, right?\N"Electric Energy"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.98,0:25:09.77,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a fuel cell, right?\N"Fuel Cells are the Energy of the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.77,0:25:10.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Right!\N"Fuel Cells are the Energy of the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.65,0:25:15.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Fuel cells are being explored as\Na next-generation energy source.\N"Fuel Cells are the Energy of the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.45,0:25:19.99,Main,,0,0,0,,They were created by thinking\Nbackward from water electrolysis.\N"Fuel Cells are the Energy of the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.99,0:25:21.87,Main,,0,0,0,,The invention of the voltaic battery\N"Fuel Cells are the Energy of the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.87,0:25:24.08,Main,,0,0,0,,led to the discovery of water electrolysis,\N"Fuel Cells are the Energy of the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.08,0:25:26.54,Main,,0,0,0,,which led to modern fuel cells!\N"Fuel Cells are the Energy of the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.54,0:25:29.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow! Mr. Volta is amazing!\N"Fuel Cells are the Energy of the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.67,0:25:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"Fuel Cells are the Energy of the Future"
